Mike Doyle (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mike_Doyle_(actor) 0 Michael Doyle (born September 16, 1972) is an American actor, screenwriter, director and producer. He may be best known for his role on Law Order: Special Victims Unit as Ryan O'Halloran. Michael_Doyle ( born September_16_,_1972 ) is an_American_actor , screenwriter , director_and_producer .
